      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and presents beautifully, offering a refined driving experience. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, while all electronic features and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service history that shows regular oil changes and preventative care. It handles with precision, shifts smoothly, and sits on a set of high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, well-documented example perfect for a buyer seeking a turn-key luxury experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
