      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm selling my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s all set to hit the road with you right away. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
