      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a cooling system refresh with a high-efficiency radiator and a valve clearance adjustment. While the aesthetics reflect a well-driven machine, the powertrain remains tight with consistent compression across all cylinders and a linear power band up to the 7,900 RPM redline.",
